OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine war: Pub dedicated 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto Hemingway destroyed in  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FKharkiv                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, You'll Never Drink Alone were the words
OL,6, that hung above the bar at the Old Hem,
OL,7, an iconic pub in the eastern Ukrainian 
OL,8, city of Kharkiv.                       
OL,10,FThe pub is named after Ernest          
OL,11,FHemingway, and its patrons would walk  
OL,12,Fpast a statue of the legendary American
OL,13,Fwriter on their way in.                
OL,15,FIt was popular among the city's young  
OL,16,Fcreatives, and Serhiy Zhadan, one of   
OL,17,FUkraine's best known poets, would often
OL,18,Fperform and drink there.               
OL,20,FBut now the Old Hem lies in ruins.     
